OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRescue loans for gas firms 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Furged over energy price    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcrisis                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is considering offering 
OL,6, emergency state-backed loans to energy 
OL,7, companies as firms battle to stay      
OL,8, afloat amid surging gas prices.        
OL,10,FBusiness Secretary Kwasi Kwarteng will 
OL,11,Fhold crisis talks with industry bosses 
OL,12,Fincluding Centrica and E.On on Monday. 
OL,14,FHigh demand for gas and reduced supply 
OL,15,Fare behind a surge in wholesale prices.
OL,17,FConsumers are protected from sudden    
OL,18,Fhikes through the government's energy  
OL,19,Fprice cap, which is the maximum price  
OL,20,Fthey can be charged.                   
